    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the overall evidence package, including Monte Carlo UQ and multi-factor evaluation, supports acceptance of the CFD hemolysis model for the VAD COU. While several factors achieved levels below required levels, the team judged the aggregate evidence sufficient given the UQ coverage and the directional correctness of predictions. Assurance level is declared Medium reflecting the breadth of the assessment.",
